{"title":"Insuficiencia cardiaca aguda","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Cardiología/Insuficiencia cardiaca aguda-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Falla cardíaca aguda\\N(FCA)","guid":"ebmsZSH2CEvRa4rdawZKvA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Resumen ","guid":"H82cEPL5bJmqC2PvnpRmsw","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Definición","guid":"","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"• ICA → Síndrome de rápida instauración o exacerbación de síntomas y signos de insuficiencia cardíaca (IC)\\N→ evaluación y tto urgente requeridos. (1).","guid":"a7r8TYmTmOHrJw1s3yAItw","children":[]}]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Historia Clínica y\\NExamen Físico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"• Factores\\NDx. Claves:","guid":"0LEMer4fwGidrQpgnkENFw","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"• Disnea","guid":"0N9qN4nqSzBMtaOVV-cBmQ","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"• Edema periférico","guid":"BomPhLeLSm5lDLoQeoAdVg","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"5","text":"• Intolerancia al ejercicio","guid":"Zmnt-Uyon8QjLPkvRKrUqQ","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"5","text":"• Fatiga","guid":"vYxoEr9VpRvql83gvLf_-w","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"5","text":"• Extremidades frías","guid":"EAfDSiyUI3mzp2b_MXkl2w","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"5","text":"• Presión venosa yugular elevada","guid":"vRgEC3tFCam3cEBL_u69vg","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"5","text":"• FC elevada, desplazamiento del choque de punta y ritmo de galope.","guid":"fiMpa1vpfoYsBceYG2ZpCA","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"4","text":"• Otros\\NFactores Dx:","guid":"YD2pcy2o84vZ8JWENsvxYA","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"• Tos nocturna, sibilancias","guid":"L8vWlLVa4KjJ4BE8CkDExA","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"• Mareos, confusión, anorexia","guid":"TsJzfGBrs2VhOJM7K847NQ","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"13","text":"• Dolor isquémico nocturno, asci