":"","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"• Gasometría venosa/arterial","guid":"RYfTDYHkXA5QsF71tKHjng","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"• Screening sanguíneo para miocarditis","guid":"QrySRbsL4ijbykBVng5-WA","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"• US torácico a la cabecera (1).","guid":"SaXjlw08V1jJbtWCQGI6Yg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"1","text":"Tratamiento","guid":"","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"1. Algoritmo de\\Ntto en ICA:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• Paciente inestable\\Nhemodinámicamente:","guid":"eY_TPG_-3d6njN6Bm6J_1Q","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"• Hipotensión o Shock cardiogénico (PA <90 mmHg)→ tto causa subyacente + considerar drogas vasoactivas,\\Nsoporte respiratorio y dispositivos de soporte mecánico → derivar a especialista.","guid":"3mWSKQV8B-UBISqImtTCyw","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"• Crisis hipertensiva → tto causa subyacente + considerar vasodilatador, diurético de asa,\\Nantagonista de aldosterona/diurético tipo tiazida → soporte respiratorio → derivar.","guid":"sWTz8QGOoJQXfqnoBatQ0g","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"37","text":"• Paciente estable\\Nhemodinámicamente:","guid":"rsWa6gTu5xEdCwQx2q6yNw","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"• tto causa subyacente + diurético de asa → considerar vasodilatador, antagonista de\\Naldosterona/diurético tiazida, β-bloqueador → soporte respiratorio → derivar a especialista.","guid":"0v-aw0-WoA0W2aTkZWoJ8w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"36","text":"2. Manejo tras estabilización\\Ndel episodio agudo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"• FEVI ≤40%:","guid":"cSE6wd_MeRPrS4clL_QZXg","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"• IECA o ARA II o sacubitril/valsartán + β-bloqueador + antagonista de aldosterona\\N+ inhibidor SGLT2 → considerar diurético → derivar + rehabilitación cardíaca.","guid":"fwsKamHGTtbNQwVDzciqmw","children":[]}]},{"id"