ción con la PA basal del paciente","guid":"J1rXFS0CVYgDqOcHyVs1ZQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"170","parent":"137","text":"Diagnóstico\\Nclínico:","guid":"8ulSXoSaIgPPbjqQ2-oY2Q","children":[{"id":"171","parent":"170","text":"Combinación de: distensión venosa yugular, galope S3 y\\Ncrepitaciones/rales en pulmones sugiere fuertemente FCA (9).","guid":"qV33EOGrnemlzeRXW2B7mg","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"170","text":"Evaluar signos de hipoperfusión (e.g., presión de pulso estrecha, extremidades frías, cianosis periférica, alteración del estado mental, PA ⬇ basal)\\Npara identificar riesgo de shock cardiogénico (3).","guid":"EClHl1FtUo0PVeGA6qc-MA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"OAczXSf6AFZBmmIxWrho3g","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"Estudios de laboratorio\\N(10)(11):","guid":"HF6j-hC0feMal8CvDf4iiw","children":[{"id":"175","parent":"174","text":"BNP o\\NNT-proBNP","guid":"clxTrDm8VeWBowkRDqjoEQ","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"Útil para confirmar diagnóstico y pronóstico","guid":"ZoASZh_1Em1-cMiYmDtkow","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"175","text":"Medición seriada para guiar la terapia (12)(13)","guid":"vwHaSVvuq119rsBBlUULCg","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"175","text":"Interpretar en relación con el valor basal del paciente, historia, examen físico e imágenes","guid":"ozlnRGE1YsgoNadl65CKqA","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"175","text":"Alta utilidad diagnóstica en casos de diagnóstico incierto (10)(11)","guid":"DKnx37uwQWKa962VNr8jHw","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"175","text":"Niveles de péptidos natriuréticos\\Nen el diagnóstico de IC (14)(8)(11):","guid":"6HDcuWq9vop2adWCRDDRNA","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"IC poco probable:","guid":"7t_eVtkWDRXamHaLOVi2sQ","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"BNP < 100 pg/mL","guid":"HgQAxafQlFAFGkpnwBTvHA","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"181","text":"NT-proBNP < 300 pg/mL","guid":"-OdBD2tulFwRsfA_Z7HkuQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"184","parent":"180","text":"IC probable:","guid":"ayL4fveOojiZXS6qIr16cg","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"BNP > 500 pg/mL","guid":"spP09-7QYEUBDlbDBB2Ftw","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"184","text":"NT-proBNP > 1000 pg/mL (11)","guid":"PMcY02B6Msz7GGgGAdnKtQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"187","parent":"174","text":"Pruebas\\Nadicionales:","guid":"wgNvs_U0LdpFwUHS-L5bRg","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"Troponina: para descartar SCA (17)","guid":"Bk2FKWPyP7vWZrBaVE8yiQ","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"187","text":"BMP (6)","guid":"TSifRgEHgTQp80RMFuMKIw","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"187","text":"Hemograma (CBC) (18)","guid":"Rkm2XDOEDxTo-r9bmBTk5g","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"187","text":"Pruebas hepáticas (19)","guid":"vE7BwXtnj0jHzA3retJ6tw","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"187","text":"Considerar pruebas de función tiroidea (6)(10)","guid":"Ov0LDL6IFraxlPLM5x5ZgA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"193","parent":"173","text":"ECG","guid":"a8qtz25zGPiU-Zrm7rZfXQ","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"Cambios isquémicos agudos por SCA","guid":"2F9ba8TKB8uPr_fdYIBgRg","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"Fibrilación auricular","guid":"kZlBPH704cPeJXc4kBmLRg","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"193","text":"Hipertrofia ventricular izquierda","guid":"KpydpM7njTEe-qwzw3F8Xg","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"193","text":"Bloqueo de rama","guid":"nMogdAQ9Q1Jk_XEJgnnRaA","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"193","text":"Cambios inespecíficos del segmento ST","guid":"FD9H7XVn9qw9NUWetPCODQ","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"193","text":"QRS de bajo voltaje (20)(21)","guid":"fyRzScGdDfrsFkF8e0tF6g","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"193","text":"ECG normal posible","guid":"lox1SuZD1H3yRU9NxnSdow","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"0","text":"Imágenes\\Niniciales","guid":"0mXtkUiXR3BKtkasiBV9Yw","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"Radiografía de\\Ntórax (6)(22):","guid":"ITmzyGvWDFTIq7u90__tMw","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"Hallazgos en edema\\Npulmonar cardiogénico:","guid":"X6RTqDc8jdvmReXcLnZ5iQ","children":[{"id":"204","parent":"203","text":"Sombra cardíaca agrandada\\N(cardiomegalia/derrame pericárdico) (23)","guid":"QEdMKOahSodDIv3EoS_0LA","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"203","text":"Líneas B de Kerley\\N(líneas septales)","guid":"HGEGeYXrCYfiTMfgM9aCiw","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"203","text":"Vasos pulmonares prominentes, edema alveolar perihiliar\\N(sombra hiliar en \"alas de mariposa\")","guid":"97lghDJdGKoy3YhDZpmi6A","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"203","text":"Edema intersticial basal","guid":"lbM33l_71nKFRKa_UtpOqQ","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"203","text":"Derrames pleurales bilaterales (24)","guid":"ZfUjeeAPRZl3h9CuzXGRsA","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"203","text":"Cefalización: vasos pulmonares prominentes en\\Nlóbulos superiores por congestión venosa (25)","guid":"ivBrc352KokYnGQtjQduSQ","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"203","text":"Engrosamiento peribronquial","guid":"T8N203Py6HGyEeubOgeMyw","children":[]}]},{"id":"211","parent":"202","text":"ABCDE en radiografía\\Nde tórax:","guid":"Z20QH8MB0I9k4XWcWCEX8Q","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"Alveolar edema (alas de murciélago)","guid":"6__KhD7cVtFfHGT7DBzFQA","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"211","text":"B Líneas de Kerley (edema intersticial)","guid":"lh8V3NqBmq60z07oOrsbAQ","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"211","text":"Cardiomegalia","guid":"saibcm9_gxijzvuYAb9yJQ","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"211","text":"Dilatación de vasos pulmonares prominentes","guid":"zWyvpi5m-O3TwtdZUmrJaQ","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"211","text":"E Derrames pleurales","guid":"XtYgTB22Knjjz_wL6KPCkw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"217","parent":"201","text":"Ecocardiograma transtorácico\\N(TTE) (6)(26):","guid":"oZVp94s2T7w7mxf1bnf5JQ","children":[{"id":"218","parent":"217","text":"Indicaciones: todos los pacientes con sospecha de FCA\\N(modalidad de imagen de elección) (27)","guid":"dciafZlKA1SIkP4nj1XjOw","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"217","text":"Hallazgos característicos\\Nen FCA:","guid":"uObKsE5AVtIfn00SK22tlg","children":[{"id":"220","parent":"219","text":"Fracción de eyección ventricular izquierda (LVEF) reducida o normal (28)","guid":"0mLGx2rD_WG8A9qXopZE3Q","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"219","text":"Disfunción diastólica","guid":"dl9b0A-a2ngPw-zfCIl8BA","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"219","text":"Dilatación auricular izquierda, trastornos valvulares (26)","guid":"gRKjzvfJytNt4yR3eSYZ6Q","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"219","text":"Derrame pericárdico","guid":"Mji4SiHMHx0Hd2G-SjK1jw","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"219","text":"Disfunción sistólica ventricular derecha, ⬆\\Npresión sistólica del ventrículo derecho","guid":"f_4np3wjatTG6hNiB3GFCg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"225","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico diferencial de la falla\\Ncardíaca aguda (FCA)","guid":"6kDns6kbncPoRW8bMH01hg","children":[{"id":"226","parent":"225","text":"1. Síndrome coronario agudo (SCA)","guid":"AT5K9Qb-1-Qo1fpd-G_UWQ","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"225","text":"2. Neumonía","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"225","text":"3. EPOC, asma","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"225","text":"4. Edema pulmonar no cardiogénico (e.g., SDRA)","guid":"ItX4Zr-MW9I3rmSZn-B1Cw","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"225","text":"5. Embolia pulmonar (EP)","guid":"R8_0sgQ8hQvz7UCpf-nSuA","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"225","text":"6. Lesión pulmonar aguda relacionada con transfusión (TRALI)","guid":"Juxu-ccCiLYZVPibxAKVFw","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"225","text":"7. Altitud elevada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"225","text":"Nota: Sibilancias pueden estar presentes tanto en FCA como en enfermedades pulmonares obstructivas\\N(e.g., exacerbación asmática, EPOC agudizada) (35).","guid":"xZ2jxCwo9oVjy677fm-W6g","children":[]}]},{"id":"234","parent":"0","text":"Manejo de la falla\\Ncardíaca aguda (FCA)","guid":"68XF2WojzheLg8Owby10qg","children":[{"id":"235","parent":"234","text":"Manejo\\Ninicial (8):","guid":"jRiLnK6SwZGaYIe26-KBqQ","children":[{"id":"236","parent":"235","text":"• Evaluar estabilidad hemodinámica mediante un rápido ABCDE.","guid":"2ypubYz8tmieJuIqmtALEQ","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"235","text":"• Identificar y tratar la causa subyacente de FCA en todos los pacientes.","guid":"F6stzqc5wt3F2QuqOmmN7A","children":[]}]},{"id":"238","parent":"234","text":"Pacientes hemodinámicamente\\Nestables:","guid":"1Raba4QS_D7u-1vCHSHUKg","children":[{"id":"239","parent":"238","text":"• Presentación clínica: PAS > 90 mm Hg y sin signos de\\Nhipoperfusión de órganos diana (puede haber disnea).","guid":"6LLVLoLpMhsdEV0myHxIPQ","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"238","text":"• Manejo (según la\\Nclasificación de FCA):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"241","parent":"240","text":"1. Sin evidencia de congestión\\N(seco y caliente):","guid":"l0jtInW15-uI3MdaA3_Ugw","children":[{"id":"242","parent":"241","text":"• Optimizar la terapia oral.","guid":"g67N_M9ZR2qbJtWgUlU3Jw","children":[]}]},{"id":"243","parent":"240","text":"2. Con evidencia de congestión\\N(húmedo y caliente):","guid":"aaOQUQ-fEV2J1ADfEC9N1Q","children":[{"id":"244","parent":"243","text":"• Soporte respiratorio inicial (e.g., posición, O2 suplementario).","guid":"o-tmn0qLIiUqnlepfwEdaw","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"243","text":"• Iniciar diuréticos (e.g., furosemida) si hay sobrecarga de volumen.","guid":"k0PbDGaM-Ei8npsBCrZlMA","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"243","text":"• Considerar vasodilatadores (e.g., nitratos).","guid":"nvNtaPGoHFd1nFzRziCK8g","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"243","text":"• La morfina no se recomienda rutinariamente (36)(8).","guid":"bMCRdrQrV6fsCnFTxQ6aDg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"248","parent":"238","text":"• Acrónimo “LMNOP”\\Npara ADHF:","guid":"CYr9Y9uSe4V6hyRBw3pgtw","children":[{"id":"249","parent":"248","text":"• L: Diuréticos de asa (furosemida)","guid":"8_5XF7yxJNwptT6Cgmc3Rw","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"248","text":"• M: Modificar medicación","guid":"KoiWQnYyzqVAnNSSsbyTVA","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"248","text":"• N: Nitratos","guid":"nVGz-eEnI80SOzfiMWeg3A","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"248","text":"• O: Oxígeno (si hipoxemia)","guid":"jrN994YVuU9hnkf8OWiAkg","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"248","text":"• P: Posición (elevar el cuerpo superior)","guid":"fNFvf1B3_XoSwwvt9qwk4Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"254","parent":"234","text":"Pacientes hemodinámicamente\\Ninestables (37):","guid":"t4t_49_kJjGb0lWCnmQiQQ","children":[{"id":"255","parent":"254","text":"• Presentación\\Nclínica:","guid":"jvEtxEh2_rEPMW1p--qhxQ","children":[{"id":"256","parent":"255","text":"1. Choque cardiogénico: PAS < 90 mm Hg o\\Nsignos de hipoperfusión de órganos diana.","guid":"NOmVC1NNzZnj4L41Dc3gkg","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"255","text":"2. Emergencia hipertensiva: PAS > 180 mm Hg +\\Nedema pulmonar flash y falla respiratoria hipoxémica.","guid":"xxMusuFSWT0z8braz_EXfw","children":[]}]},{"id":"258","parent":"254","text":"• Manejo (según la\\Nclasificación de FCA):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"259","parent":"258","text":"1. Congestión con choque\\N(húmedo y frío):","guid":"1GOnFtDXOANPuY2qsgiolA","children":[{"id":"260","parent":"259","text":"• Priorizar soporte respiratorio.","guid":"qCw4yZZM9UkPsX10AnJzSA","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"259","text":"• Considerar soporte inotrópico (e.g., dobutamina, norepinefrina).","guid":"4jT9Z6WQ1otlrCEl4Jt_Tg","children":[]}]},{"id":"262","parent":"258","text":"2. Choque sin congestión\\N(seco y frío):","guid":"t2cAlSeP-gdVXVWmUMgIFA","children":[{"id":"263","parent":"262","text":"• Considerar reto con fluidos.","guid":"HL5KCGNPLhhu0LH40NuTRg","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"262","text":"• Agregar vasopresores e inotrópicos si el choque es refractario a fluidos.","guid":"d4QdvrixF5vad2FR45s0KQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"265","parent":"258","text":"3. Emergencia hipertensiva con edema pulmonar flash\\N(húmedo y caliente):","guid":"F_6ExMtLo36FqFKbS3iKtA","children":[{"id":"266","parent":"265","text":"• Iniciar NIPPV y vasodilatadores.","guid":"CBAV0kGnn_PRNGDJqEmIVQ","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"265","text":"• Identificar y tratar el desencadenante subyacente (38)(39)(36).","guid":"ChBsZjGmH2YoclV9Xt6WTg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"268","parent":"234","text":"Manejo hospitalario\\Ncontinuo","guid":"5FHbhuVrxqBvV-SSFxhjNA","children":[{"id":"269","parent":"268","text":"Cuidado de\\Nsoporte:","guid":"0Q8f7l_TsF7skl6eX_GMkA","children":[{"id":"270","parent":"269","text":"• Restricción de líquidos no reduce hospitalización ni mortalidad en pacientes con IC (6).","guid":"gAdgDs7bXcmoTI4ZehQQPQ","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"269","text":"• Restricción de sodio (6).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"269","text":"• Identificar y tratar comorbilidades (e. g., FA, neumonía, EPOC) y desencadenantes subyacentes.","guid":"QCdY32BHCWwgpVHo_B5WeQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"273","parent":"268","text":"Optimización de la terapia crónica\\Npara IC crónica (6)(8)(3):","guid":"D2UTUJxzK7SL9lDF6HMJXg","children":[{"id":"274","parent":"273","text":"1. Betabloqueantes:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"275","parent":"274","text":"• Administrar con precaución en pacientes que no usaban BB previamente.","guid":"r-VysrU-rfwtWCnzK5NLRA","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"274","text":"• Iniciar a dosis bajas.","guid":"jr1XmOuLXuYfbK_OS1V9gg","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"274","text":"• Administrar solo tras estabilización (e.g., luego de optimizar el estado de volumen\\Ny suspender diuréticos IV, vasodilatadores y agentes inotrópicos) (36)(8).","guid":"LFoKChOWJjRAYUf_X0nDUw","children":[]}]},{"id":"278","parent":"273","text":"2. Tratamiento médico de la IC:","guid":"LeSU1FRrP7njm-YD7BkG5Q","children":[{"id":"279","parent":"278","text":"• Iniciar, ajustar o continuar según necesidad.","guid":"2n_eLkpFaPKwZm5WcWj48g","children":[]}]},{"id":"280","parent":"273","text":"3. Control de PA: Optimizar (ver manejo de HTA).","guid":"lFn5Knw-Ifoff0yMFCKeqA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"281","parent":"234","text":"Tratamiento de FCA\\Nrefractaria (8):","guid":"2ScKKMV0A0RKP14ZHMbARg","children":[{"id":"282","parent":"281","text":"• Ultrafiltración (e.g., hemodiálisis): Indicada en congestión que no responde a terapia médica.","guid":"YPi-vssDw2olF-OjGwt7yw","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"281","text":"• Soporte circulatorio mecánico: Indicado en IC aguda reversible y refractaria (37)(46).","guid":"YTp7UiqxjGeWXkevaduMzg","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"281","text":"• Manejo de derrames: Considerar toracocentesis o pericardiocentesis terapéutica según necesidad.","guid":"e_dUIkETyfIVk9jqV8h7UQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"285","parent":"0","text":"Soporte respiratorio en la falla\\Ncardíaca aguda (FCA)","guid":"n8FNlft2adE231JNB8bWYg","children":[{"id":"286","parent":"285","text":"Medidas\\Niniciales (8):","guid":"Ib-hro-gu5rGrTFhy2EYOA","children":[{"id":"287","parent":"286","text":"1. Posición: Mantener al paciente en posición sentada (49).","guid":"7rwn5QtC8OhxWOXgcukheA","children":[]},{"id":"288","parent":"286","text":"2. Oxígeno suplementario: Indicado en pacientes con SpO2 < 90% o PaO2 < 60 mm Hg\\N(ver “Terapia de oxígeno”).","guid":"ohfwbHSBQs2Sj-BQsRKHcA","children":[]}]},{"id":"289","parent":"285","text":"Falla\\Nrespiratoria:","guid":"ZZuR2nz-7m-PgBFCzw2_cA","children":[{"id":"290","parent":"289","text":"1. NIPPV: Indicado en pacientes con dificultad\\Nrespiratoria a pesar de oxígeno suplementario (8).","guid":"OTS6iOi7djNXS2lfaAolQg","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"289","text":"2. Ventilación\\Nmecánica invasiva:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"292","parent":"291","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"SbdHpRlVneMUWEweYs6-tg","children":[{"id":"293","parent":"292","text":"• Falla respiratoria hipoxémica no responsiva a NIPPV.","guid":"FRO6zB9kAEL6kUr-ohaVnw","children":[]},{"id":"294","parent":"292","text":"• Hipoxemia refractaria (PaO2 < 60 mm Hg).","guid":"3ok94BPjHvF_xe5FRhZQdg","children":[]},{"id":"295","parent":"292","text":"• Hipercapnia (PaCO2 > 50 mm Hg).","guid":"ZFQgL9__2Wb6x2grY3k1HA","children":[]},{"id":"296","parent":"292","text":"• Acidosis (pH < 7.35).","guid":"bzIK8407BClKuG-0j93-ZQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"297","parent":"285","text":"Precaución: Usar EPAP y/o PEEP con cuidado\\Nen pacientes con compromiso hemodinámico.","guid":"1sCMFTXcI42-No3YYT8sFg","children":[]}]},{"id":"298","parent":"0","text":"Farmacoterapia","guid":"_UAa-e8bSCpisZ7YPofLiA","children":[{"id":"299","parent":"298","text":"Terapia\\Ndiurética","guid":"JGoDPLdsrD2UkndqE04POg","children":[{"id":"300","parent":"299","text":"Tratamiento\\Ninicial:","guid":"BaIjOQjsEeKLhACVEi-vew","children":[{"id":"301","parent":"300","text":"• Administrar diuréticos por vía IV si es posible.","guid":"5Z_bA7JTbnSZpY7OcHAlZg","children":[]},{"id":"302","parent":"300","text":"• Pacientes sin tratamiento diurético previo: Furosemida IV o bumetanida.","guid":"0c6R8Xm7-_QuyKP8nKCQkQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"303","parent":"299","text":"Tratamiento\\Ncontinuo:","guid":"Ig6t89SI_gdTB1uvvrI9ng","children":[{"id":"304","parent":"303","text":"• Ajuste de dosis: Evaluar efecto de diuréticos (e.g., diuresis, síntomas) cada 6 horas.","guid":"3rMaM0QQnTSl65vSK3VEcQ","children":[]},{"id":"305","parent":"303","text":"• FCA refractaria (a pesar de dosis\\Naltas de diuréticos de asa):\\NConsiderar lo siguiente:","guid":"BcCsQmYoSN5ialYlKYlGnw","children":[{"id":"306","parent":"305","text":"• Terapia combinada con un diurético tiazídico (e.g.,\\Nmetolazona, hidroclorotiazida, clorotiazida) (6)(56).","guid":"l7yuDZ--0_lpFNoL5bRozA","children":[]},{"id":"307","parent":"305","text":"• Adición de un vasodilatador (6).","guid":"Nhj_gKMZY07oqj8SYaY_7A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"308","parent":"299","text":"Monitoreo:","guid":"7hZUQ06scIYyt41Ca2a5BA","children":[{"id":"309","parent":"308","text":"• Monitorear y reponer\\Nelectrolitos séricos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"310","parent":"308","text":"• Monitorear función renal\\N(niveles de creatinina).","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"311","parent":"298","text":"Terapia\\Nvasodilatadora","guid":"Y12VBsAUc9ASJZ-mrvbAHQ","children":[{"id":"312","parent":"311","text":"Indicaciones\\N(6)(8):","guid":"MuebDZOtEc2XXQ5ZyVZsiw","children":[{"id":"313","parent":"312","text":"• FCA causada por emergencia hipertensiva\\N(ver “Tratamiento de crisis hipertensivas”)","guid":"NeKZAdzeTCb0LcZX2OdcWg","children":[]},{"id":"314","parent":"312","text":"• Edema pulmonar flash.","guid":"vfGoYS5ptzoRf_mOCpBI1A","children":[]},{"id":"315","parent":"312","text":"• Adyuvante a diuréticos para alivio sintomático de disnea (6).","guid":"KxvMR7NVlFvf0fZyg1Xicg","children":[]}]},{"id":"316","parent":"311","text":"Opciones de\\Ntratamiento (6):","guid":"p8qt2wTX7fVN0mpL_D-Y6A","children":[{"id":"317","parent":"316","text":"• Nitroglicerina IV.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"318","parent":"316","text":"• Nitroprusiato de sodio.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"319","parent":"316","text":"• Si hay contraindicaciones para nitroglicerina, considerar nesiritida (36).","guid":"y1r00bKPU17_JSRhLtw2BA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"320","parent":"298","text":"Precaución: Evitar vasodilatadores en pacientes con FCA e hipotensión.","guid":"f5DH4BVQ6w2wx_u7GeqqkA","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":320,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Cardiología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Cardiología","filename":"Insuficiencia cardiaca aguda-2024-1","id":"map_298","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Insuficiencia cardiaca aguda-2024-1"}